qas.question: What types of taxes do Puerto Ricans pay?
What makes up the federal taxes Puerto Rican citizens pay?

answers.text: import/export taxes, federal commodity taxes, social security taxes

qas.question: How else can they serve the U.S.?

answers.text: Puerto Ricans may enlist in the U.S. military.
